snippet.title: Solbot Enery Rush
snippet.description:
Solbot Energy Rush is a casual and fun Mobile Game. Play as a robot and collect renewable energy resources as part of a space mission. 

Playstore: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.freakoutgames.chromaflyer&referrer=utm_source%3Dyoutube

AppStore: https://itunes.apple.com/app/apple-store/id1368418939?pt=118751688&ct=youtube&mt=8

Checkout the website:
https://solbot.weebly.com/

Get connected:
https://twitter.com/FreakoutGames
https://www.facebook.com/freakoutgames/
